{
  "texts": [
    "Case studydeveloped a debiased recommender system that mitigates gender bias in college major recommendations 2.",
    "Conducted an online user study with over 200 student participants.",
    "-Dataset with information from 16,619 anonymised Facebook users; 60% female and 40% male, 1,380 unique college majors, 143,303 unique items that a user can like on Facebook and 3.5 million + useritem pairs.",
    "-Online user study with 202 participants: 48% females and 49.5% males.",
    "Only 18.3% open to career suggestions -Constructed user embedding via Neural collaborative filtering (NCF) model for predicting the items a user \"likes\"."
  ]
}